# Build artefacts (anywhere in the tree).
*.agdai
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.toc
*~

# Handoff notes / internal markdown are kept locally but not tracked.
# (The root README.md is exempted by the whitelist below.)
*.md

# Reference / generated PDFs are kept locally but not tracked.
*.pdf

# Whitelist policy: only the following files/dirs are tracked.
#   /BRA4/           -- the active Agda codebase (.agda + .tex sources only)
#   /bra-godelII.tex -- the project paper / writeup
#   /README.md       -- public project README
#
# Everything else (including CLAUDE.md, BRA/ and BRA2/ legacy editions,
# BRA4/*.md handoff notes, *.pdf references, build artefacts, and /old/)
# is untracked.

/*

!/.gitignore
!/BRA4/
!/bra-godelII.tex
!/README.md
